%section#please-donate.paper
  #results.handwritten
    To date #{results[:users]} people + #{results[:companies]} companies
    have donated
    %em= number_to_currency(results[:total])
    in total.
    This puts a huge :D on our face. We love you guys.

  %h2.ribbon Please donate!
  %p Donating to a fun project should be even more fun than just fun. So we made it <em>fun</em> :)
  %p
    We've got some
    %a{href: '#stickers'} awesome stickers
    hot off the press as well as a bunch of
    %a{href: '#ringtones'} ringtones and sounds
    from  Yehuda, Aaron, Jose and Jon. And how about a virtual cup of tea with Josh and Sven on Skype or even a one hour remote pairing session with one of our fantastic volunteers!
    %sup 1
  %p You can get these packages in two flavors: as one-off payments or subscriptions. Flip the switch on the right to review them:
  .switch
    %label.on{for: 'type_package', value: 'packages'} One off
    %label{for: 'type_subscription', value: 'subscriptions'} Subscription

  #packages
    %h3 Packages
    %ul.packages.clearfix
      %li.tiny
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:tiny)
        %h4 Tiny
        %p A cool Travis CI sticker and access to the ringtones and sounds.
        - if stats[:tiny]
          %p.stats
            %span= "#{stats[:tiny]} people donated."
        = link_to 'Donate', new_package_path(package: 'tiny')
      %li.small
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:small)
        %h4 Small
        %p 3 stickers, access to ringtones &amp; sounds.
        %p Plus: a personal thank you from the Travis CI team
        - if stats[:tiny]
          %p.stats
            %span= "#{stats[:tiny]} people donated."
        = link_to 'Donate', new_package_path(package: 'small')
      %li.medium
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:medium)
        %h4 Medium
        %p All the stuff from the previous plan with all the Travis CI stickers.
        %p Plus: you get on the waiting list for Travis CI pro beta access.
        - if stats[:tiny]
          %p.stats
            %span= "#{stats[:tiny]} people donated."
        = link_to 'Donate', new_package_path(package: 'medium')
      %li.big
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:big)
        %h4 Big
        %p All the stuff from the previous plan.
        %p Plus: 50 EUR credit for your future Travis CI pro account.
        %p And a skype cup of tea with Josh &amp; Sven.
        - if stats[:tiny]
          %p.stats
            %span= "#{stats[:tiny]} people donated."
        = link_to 'Donate', new_package_path(package: 'big')
      %li.huge
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:huge)
        %h4 Huge
        %p All the stuff from the previous plan plus:
        %p 200 EUR credit for your future Travis CI pro account.
        %p
          And 1 hour remote pairing or support with one of our volunteers
          %sup> 1
          \.
        - if stats[:tiny]
          %p.stats
            %span= "#{stats[:tiny]} people donated."
        = link_to 'Donate', new_package_path(package: 'huge')

  #subscriptions
    %h3 Subscriptions
    %ul.packages.clearfix
      %li.tiny
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:tiny, true)
        %h4 Tiny
        %p A cool Travis CI sticker and access to the ringtones and sounds.
        = link_to 'Donate', new_subscription_path(package: 'tiny')
      %li.small
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:small, true)
        %h4 Small
        %p 3 stickers, access to ringtones &amp; sounds.
        %p Plus: a personal thank you from the Travis CI team
        = link_to 'Donate', new_subscription_path(package: 'small')
      %li.medium
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:medium, true)
        %h4 Medium
        %p All the stuff from the previous plan with all the Travis CI stickers.
        %p Plus: you get on the waiting list for Travis CI pro beta access.
        = link_to 'Donate', new_subscription_path(package: 'medium')
      %li.big
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:big, true)
        %h4 Big
        %p All the stuff from the previous plan.
        %p Plus: 50 EUR credit for your future Travis CI pro account.
        %p And a skype cup of tea with Josh &amp; Sven.
        = link_to 'Donate', new_subscription_path(package: 'big')
      %li.huge
        .price-tag
          = number_to_currency Package.price(:huge, true)
        %h4 Huge
        %p All the stuff from the previous plan plus:
        %p 200 EUR credit for your future Travis CI pro account.
        %p
          And 1 hour remote pairing or support with one of our volunteers
          %sup> 1
          \.
        = link_to 'Donate', new_subscription_path(package: 'huge')

